extendedInfo.description: Join us for the 9th annual CHC Safety & Quality Summit, March 18-20, 2013 in Vancouver, B.C., Canada. You will find exceptional speakers on our program plus plenty of time for networking and dialogue. We invite you to attend as many sessions as you can to get the most out of the Summit as we explore the theme of "Building an Accident Free Legacy: Predictive Safety to Avoid 'the Inevitable'".
